article.headline: Phillips scores 19 in UNC Wilmington's 81-65 victory over William & Mary
article.description: — Shykeim Phillips scored 19 points as UNC Wilmington beat William & Mary 81-65 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Phillips scores 19 in UNC Wilmington's 81-65 victory over William & Mary
article.story: WILLIAMSBURG, Va. -- — Shykeim Phillips scored 19 points as UNC Wilmington beat William & Mary 81-65 on Thursday night. Phillips also added five assists and three steals for the Seahawks (20-7, 11-4 Coastal Athletic Association). KJ Jenkins shot 7 for 14, including 4 for 11 from beyond the arc to add 18 points. Trazarien White had 14 points and shot 3 of 8 from the field and 7 for 8 from the line. Maleeck Harden-Hayes also had 14 points. Caleb Dorsey led the way for the Tribe (8-20, 3-12) with 14 points. Trey Moss added 12 points for William & Mary. In addition, Sean Houpt finished with nine points. The loss was the Tribe's seventh in a row. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
